  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3078960/extras/f3248eea85a1fd5fa580cb1d1a8ff433.poster.avif?t=1729060005\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3078960/extras/f3248eea85a1fd5fa580cb1d1a8ff433.webm?t=1729060005\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3078960/extras/f3248eea85a1fd5fa580cb1d1a8ff433.mp4?t=1729060005\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >DiggerSim - Excavator Simulator is a thrilling excavator and heavy equipment simulator that puts you in the driver's seat of a powerful excavator. With realistic controls, you'll feel like you're really operating heavy machinery. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Excavation Tasks</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > DiggerSim PC offers a wide range of levels that progressively challenge your abilities. Each level presents unique obstacles and objectives that will test your skills to the utmost, ensuring that you don't need to be a professional excavator operator—just plug in and play.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3078960/extras/57eb1ea0fd787fd89b83604cc70d09ac.poster.avif?t=1729060005\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3078960/extras/57eb1ea0fd787fd89b83604cc70d09ac.webm?t=1729060005\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3078960/extras/57eb1ea0fd787fd89b83604cc70d09ac.mp4?t=1729060005\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Excavator Movement</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > With responsive, controls that emulate the real thing, you can take complete charge of your excavator. You'll feel as though you're controlling a heavy machinery thanks to the realistic movement dynamics, whether you're navigating around obstacles. All movements, arm swings, were designed to deliver an authentic and fun experience.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3078960/extras/33a10afb6fb6b8fa2998a3dfa822c0ba.poster.avif?t=1729060005\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3078960/extras/33a10afb6fb6b8fa2998a3dfa822c0ba.webm?t=1729060005\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3078960/extras/33a10afb6fb6b8fa2998a3dfa822c0ba.mp4?t=1729060005\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Realistic Digging Mechanism</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Discover DiggerSim's actual digging. You can feel the weight of every scoop and bucket movement as you dig trenches, foundations, and more. Because of the mechanics in the game, your actions have an actual impact on the surroundings.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As you progress through the game, you'll have challenges that will test your skills and abilities. With immersive gameplay and realistic controls, Digger Sim is the ultimate experience for fans of construction and heavy machinery. So put on your hard hat and get ready to dig in!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Controller Suggested</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > To fully appreciate the accuracy and realism of handling heavy machinery, we recommend utilising a controller for the most realistic experience. Every excavation work will feel authentic thanks to the controller's lifelike movements and reactions, which are made easy to use with intuitive controls.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3078960/extras/9f79090c0147ba176788eefdbe92fa2f.poster.avif?t=1729060005\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3078960/extras/9f79090c0147ba176788eefdbe92fa2f.webm?t=1729060005\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3078960/extras/9f79090c0147ba176788eefdbe92fa2f.mp4?t=1729060005\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Join our Discord channel!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
